<p style="font-size: 13px;">Before you accept the “Buy Now” price it is your responsibility to do the following:</p>
<p style="font-size: 13px;">Verify buyer has inspected the property or show them property.</p>
<p style="font-size: 13px;">Verify their proof of funds and/or Hard Money pre-approval.</p>
<p style="font-size: 13px;">Verify that your property has clear title.</p>
<p style="font-size: 13px;">Get buyer to sign your Sales or Assignment Contract, collect the earnest money/deposit and open title.</p>
<p style="font-size: 13px;">You don’t have a solid deal until you get the above confirmed so please do your own due diligence.</p>
